---
---

<section id="setup" class="section bg-apple-bg-alt/50">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="fade-up text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-apple-text tracking-tight">
        Give us five minutes.<br />We'll give you <em class="italic">5000.</em>
      </h2>
      <p class="fade-up text-lg text-apple-text-secondary mt-4 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Writers Room is 20x faster than traditional search, despite giving you better results. We index your notes from anywhere. Apple Notes. Bear. Ulysses. Random markdown folders. Takes a few minutes, but you'll never search the same again.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="fade-up space-y-6 max-w-lg mx-auto">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="flex items-start gap-5">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-apple-text text-apple-bg text-sm font-bold flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">1</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-apple-text mb-1">Download</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-apple-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Drag Writers Room to your Applications folder. That's it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Connector -->
      <div class="ml-5 h-4 border-l border-apple-border/40"></div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="flex items-start gap-5">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-apple-text text-apple-bg text-sm font-bold flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">2</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-apple-text mb-1">Add your API key</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-apple-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Open settings and setup any AI provider of your choice. We natively support Groq, OpenAI, Mistral, and others. Just put your API key in. Don't worry, we'll show you how to get one.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Connector -->
      <div class="ml-5 h-4 border-l border-apple-border/40"></div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="flex items-start gap-5">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-apple-text text-apple-bg text-sm font-bold flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">3</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-apple-text mb-1">Index your notes</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-apple-text-secondary leading-relaxed">One click. Writers Room reads your notes and builds a local search index. If you have a large library it could take a few minutes. But after that, it stays in sync.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Connector -->
      <div class="ml-5 h-4 border-l border-apple-border/40"></div>

      <!-- Step 4 -->
      <div class="flex items-start gap-5">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-apple-text text-apple-bg text-sm font-bold flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">4</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-apple-text mb-1">Search</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-apple-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Hit your shortcut. Type what you remember. Find what you forgot.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="fade-up text-center mt-12">
      <a
        href="#"
        class="inline-flex items-center px-10 py-4 bg-apple-text text-apple-bg text-lg font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-apple-text/85 transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-black/10"
      >
        Download for Mac
      </a>
      <p class="text-sm text-apple-text-secondary mt-4">
        macOS 13 Ventura or later. Apple Silicon and Intel.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
